  "summary": "Provides an authoring interface on the Course page that exposes inline editing controls for sections and activities and a modal Activity Chooser for adding new activities or resources.",
  "where_it_fits": "This module is part of the Course Page experience: when a user viewing a course (via Home > My Courses or Dashboard > My Courses) enables Edit mode, the course page switches to this authoring UI and the Activity Chooser modal is launched from the \"+ Add an activity or resource\" control within course sections.",
